name: Change Home Store from the home page - Using Current Location
description: User tries to change home store using current location
descriptionHtml: User tries to change home store using current location

testStage.description: User tries to change home store using current location

steps.name: I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I mock the location of the device to "CORNWALL_800786"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "CORNWALL_800786" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "CORNWALL_800786" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I click on "CHANGE STORE" button
I check that the "Want to change store?" pane is displayed
I click on "USE CURRENT LOCATION" button
I get the text from the "STATION ADDRESS"
I check that the application text: "1330 SECOND ST. E." is equals to expected value: "1330 SECOND ST. E."
I click on "CHANGE STORE" button
I check that the "Want to change store?" pane is displayed
I get the text "Want to change store?" from the bottom sheet pane
I check that the application text: "Want to change store?" is equals to expected value: "Want to change store?"
I check that "USE CURRENT LOCATION" button is displayed
I check that "SELECT STORE MANUALLY" button is displayed
